            <lg xml:id="TK576">
<l>maṇṇō ṭiyainta marattaṉaiyar kaṇṇō </l>
<l>ṭiyaintukaṇ ṇōṭā tavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They resemble the trees of the earth, who although they have eyes, never look kindly (on others).</l>
